Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.58,0:00:09.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,The countless flowers,\Nenveloped in light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.69,0:00:20.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,...gaze at tomorrow\Nwith unwavering eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:38.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everyone wishes for me to be pure...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.46,0:00:46.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,...but what can I bring\Nwith me to the frayed skies?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.66,0:00:53.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,What I've made my own\Nby breaking off flowers in bloom...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.04,0:00:59.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,All such sinful things...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.41,0:01:06.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why did I stop making\Npromises with the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.88,0:01:14.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because even if I try\Nto run far from all the pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:20.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,...a cold wind rustles\Nmy hair... Don't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.90,0:01:28.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where can I ever find the answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:43.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,With the death of Sibylla Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.59,0:01:47.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and the ancient Simouns\Nnow in the hands of Shoukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.19,0:01:49.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you could say they've\Nleveled the playing field.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.56,0:01:52.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, considering their\Nbattle expertise...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,...they now pose a\Nconsiderable threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:55.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:58.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was reckless to send in\NChor Tempest after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.50,0:02:03.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,But Chor Tempest did cause damage\Nto the aerial base, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:07.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy will need\Ntime to regroup...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.34,0:02:09.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,...so I hardly think they'll\Nbe attacking anytime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.91,0:02:12.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,That sibylla's death\Nbought us some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:14.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.19,0:02:21.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Remember that Tempus Spatium is\Nwatching over everything you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:29.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Lament
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:57.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominüra...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:58.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and Rimone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.29,0:02:59.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I bet they're dead too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.66,0:03:01.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.43,0:03:05.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,They all...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.93,0:03:07.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,They all died!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,And it's going to keep happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:11.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:13.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're all going to die.\NI just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:21.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:22.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:27.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,War is just a name\Nfor killing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:30.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you can't accept that, then you\Nneed to go to the Spring right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why... did it\Nhave to be Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:57.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why... did it\Nhave to be Mamina?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:02.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't even shed tears over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:05.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,The day Amuria died...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:09.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think that maybe my own\Nheart died along with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've caused others pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:17.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Rejected their advances...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:23.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yet despite it all, here I am,\Nunable to shed a tear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:25.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Living on with a heart\Nthat's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.05,0:04:28.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:32.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,If only I'd died instead of Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:48.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.68,0:04:58.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you been here all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Have you been crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,If only...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:09.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I'd been stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina wouldn't have died!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:17.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,If only I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.40,0:05:18.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:21.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm the one to blame,\Nbecause I was her pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,You had nothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.54,0:05:26.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't say that I had\Nnothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,What happened to the Aer who\Nwasn't afraid of anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:55.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:57.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I said I want to become stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.74,0:05:59.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,You understand, right, Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've got to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:14.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I... I've got to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:19.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,To live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.27,0:06:28.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Behind me lies the finest sibylla\Nin all of Simulacrum Kyuukoku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:30.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Sibylla Aurea Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:33.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm getting her out\Nof here no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:37.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,And not one of you will lay\Nso much as a finger on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:39.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:41.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,We've got to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you want something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:30.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Patch things up? That sounds like\Nwe were actually friends before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:34.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,Till the end, one of us\Nwill always be above...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and the other below.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:40.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just what were\Nyou thinking that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.41,0:07:43.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,That I wanted to be friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:50.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's because I really want\Nto be friends with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:55.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:58.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,So stop saying things like,\N"We're friends," will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just a matter of\Nhow you feel about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.46,0:08:01.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:03.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll stop then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:21.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have summoned\NOnasia from the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,And the military council?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:26.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,As you have ordered,\Nthey know nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:31.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,They only have eyes for warfare.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is truly deplorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:38.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hatred has tarnished the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:41.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,And yet they still cling to\Nthis meaningless dispute...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.70,0:08:45.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...which can only lead to mutual\Nannihilation in battle. Such foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:49.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is no time to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:53.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,We must find our way out of this\Ncursed land as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:55.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,We must follow the path\Nof Tempus Spatium...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and open the door\Nto a new world!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,A new world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.46,0:09:02.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, and to that end...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Anubituf...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:07.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,There is much that I must\Nask you to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.13,0:09:08.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,First of all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:10.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,The phantom chor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra must be resurrected!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.54,0:09:22.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Granted, they're somewhat inferior\Nto the Simouns in performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:25.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,But other than that, there\Nare no major differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:29.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is Sibylla Neviril's Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:39.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:42.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dismantling the ancient\NSimoun's your priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,All else will have\Nto wait, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.03,0:09:47.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, not that I'm\Nblaming you or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:50.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can't rebel\Nagainst your superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:51.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:54.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was what I\Nwanted to do as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:58.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Morinas...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Would you please\Ngo to the Spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:12.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't do that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Simouns are cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't care about the Simouns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:19.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,"As long as I can fly a\NSimoun, nothing else matters!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:25.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Who cares about my comrades?"\NAt least, that's what I used to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it seems I was\Nwrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:30.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've changed, Sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:34.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,So have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Now that Mamina's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:55.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,...do you think they're going\Nto reshuffle our pairs again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:58.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.64,0:11:02.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,But for all of us to pair up...\Nwe're short one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you think, Para-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:11.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.49,0:11:14.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:17.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I don't have any\Nanswers for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.73,0:11:22.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.23,0:11:29.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina is dead. How do\NI tell her I'm sorry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.57,0:11:32.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,All I could think about\Nwas my own problems...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:36.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and I wasn't performing as\Na member of Chor Tempest should.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:39.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.68,0:11:42.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since when? And how?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:44.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,How did I come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:46.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:48.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.86,0:11:53.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:11:58.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn't have to be for real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:11:59.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.27,0:12:02.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just be Para-sama,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.97,0:12:08.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if they're wrong,\Njust make bold decisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know you're\Nsuffering too, Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:12.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:16.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,By simply being our\Nheroic Para-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:19.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,...you give us all\Na little bit of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:22.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,You say "us all," but\Nyou mean Kaim, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:27.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why would you go so far for Kaim?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to see\Nmy sister smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.90,0:12:31.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,The reason why I wanted\Nto become a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why I wanted to become stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:36.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was all because I wanted\Nto make my sister happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I finally realized something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,That something's keeping\Nmy sister from smiling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and it's because\NI'm in her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:56.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,And if that's the case, there's\Nonly one thing I can do for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,For my sister's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.97,0:13:07.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I'll separate myself from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.38,0:13:18.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:19.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Paraietta-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:21.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's Sibylla Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:23.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:39.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:42.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe! What are you\Ndoing with that suitcase?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:44.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:45.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you mean you're going?\NI'm going to the Spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:46.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the Spring!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.41,0:13:49.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's no use trying to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:52.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I have no intention\Nof going to war...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.28,0:13:53.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,...and I have no\Nintention of dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:56.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold on! We should all\Ntalk about this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:23.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,What, for heaven's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:26.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is it a patrol Simile?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:28.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Where would it be\Ngoing at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Mamina's\Nremains have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:46.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,...sent to her land where\Nshe was born and raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,But why? Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:55.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,It was the high priestess's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:59.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,She felt that in order to\Ncomfort Sibylla Mamina's soul...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.15,0:15:02.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it would be best to return\Nher to her beloved homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.68,0:15:07.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you could've done that after her\Nfuneral service here on the Arcus Prima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:09.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.13,0:15:13.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,As a Simoun sibylla\Nwho died with honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:16.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,...it was our job to see that\Nshe was given a proper burial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.70,0:15:18.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Died... with honor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.97,0:15:20.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:30.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Vura. In place\Nof Sibylla Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.65,0:15:33.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,...she will be flying\Na Simoun with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.55,0:15:34.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,But wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.88,0:15:38.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is imperative that we rearrange\Nyour pairs as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:42.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,As well as achieve even\Nmore powerful Ri Majons.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.36,0:15:44.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,Military Councilor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:47.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,We have just lost one\Nof our precious comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:51.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ri Majons require our souls to be clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:54.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,We must be able to pray\Nwith the purest of minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.27,0:15:55.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,We are not ready...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,You speak as if you have\Nno cares in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:02.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you wish Sibylla Mamina\Nto have died in vain?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:16.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:28.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just too cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.47,0:16:30.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,How could they not let\Nus even say goodbye?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.97,0:16:33.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,The military councilor's\Nno different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.64,0:16:37.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,All he can think about is war. He's not\Nreally thinking about Mamina at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.02,0:16:44.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's because Mamina...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because she wasn't from\Na Simoun sibylla family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:53.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just like Mamina said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:56.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm just a pampered\Nrich girl after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.73,0:16:58.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,And Mamina's feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.50,0:17:00.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:01.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,But it turns out I\Ndidn't understand a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.84,0:17:06.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you want to understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:08.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:12.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina's feelings...\NThey're right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:26.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,It resides here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:29.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,...Sibylla Mamina's soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:36.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,And this soul... it has\Naccepted that her life is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:37.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:41.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,In her eyes, it was\Na meaningful death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:42.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:45.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,You mustn't touch Onasia-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:48.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bring it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.68,0:17:49.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,"Accepted that her life is over?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:59.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,I hate when people\Nsay things like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:00.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's just to make\Nus feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:05.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,How can anyone really know\Nwhat the dead are feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:07.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:21.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was always envious of\Nthose braids of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,But these are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.52,0:18:27.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,You plait your hair because\Nyour parents told you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.36,0:18:31.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,But those things don't\Nmean a thing to a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:35.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,To me, they were a\Nrich girl's hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,That day...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:42.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,...I really wanted to\Nbe friends with Mamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:46.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just what do you\Nthink you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.54,0:18:51.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,She really wanted to\Nbe friends with us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.86,0:19:04.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.19,0:19:06.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:24.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamina is a Simoun sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.75,0:19:26.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:32.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,And we Simoun sibylla didn't\Ncome here to go to war!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:36.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.56,0:19:38.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:40.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:41.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roatreamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:44.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:52.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,For all of you to go, you\Nneed one more person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.58,0:19:56.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of my Rubor comrades\Nhave gone to the Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.18,0:19:59.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I decided to\Nstay here anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:01.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,...for the same reason Mamina did!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I wanted to\Nstay a Simoun sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.79,0:20:11.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Vura... thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:26.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:28.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:36.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What on earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:39.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's allowing them\Nto take such liberties?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:49.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,How dare they,\Nin a time of emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll begin with one\Nthat Mamina excelled at...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:57.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the Wave Crest Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:10.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next, let's do the\NDandelion Ri Majon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.60,0:21:23.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just as we thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.00,0:21:24.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:30.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right! We're all...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.11,0:21:33.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aer...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:51.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:54.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who inscribe our\Nprayers across the skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.30,0:22:01.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.54,0:22:08.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,We pray for the future that\Nwill go on forever and ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.31,0:22:13.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,And for the past that we've\Nalready woven, we offer our prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:20.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibyllae...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.62,0:22:23.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.66,0:22:26.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's who we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.14,0:22:47.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,It is played by my wounds...\Nthe song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:52.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let it ring out over\Nthe grieving universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.12,0:22:59.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can we change tomorrow?\NDon't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.19,0:23:06.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to let you know\Nhow my heart's overflowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:19.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to get closer to you.\NI want to feel your pulse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:24.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was too defiant,\Nand I took the long way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:28.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,The blue moon is swaying silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.82,0:23:32.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,My true heart's desire is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.86,0:23:38.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can't reach you.\NMy tears of pain trickle down.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.73,0:23:44.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Soar away into the\Nsky, song of prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:47.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Carrying my love that came too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.71,0:23:53.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,What can I do to change tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.38,0:23:59.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just hold on to "now" the way it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.86,0:24:06.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,To Be Continued
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:09.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bestowed upon us by Tempus Spatium...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.60,0:24:11.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,...the other "if."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.43,0:24:15.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Next time on Simoun...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.40,0:24:15.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Door to a New World
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.77,0:24:17.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Door to a New World\NThe Door to a New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.67,0:24:19.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Door to a New World
